Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is rushing to Navy HQ to rescue his brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace who will be executed in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the Whitebeard \NPirates storming Marineford...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...begin an all-out war with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb Oars' body and advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Team Arrives! Tension \NGrows at the Battlefield"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a chill in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, partner! Can't you do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that \Nwax will help in any way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are Luffy and the others \Nfalling from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go back a little bit in \Ntime to know what happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship that they were on was \Nhit by Whitebeard's seaquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's really big!\N--We're gonna get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea just suddenly drew back and now there's a big tsunami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimbei! We gotta do something or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be defeated \Nby a tsunami here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I gotta save Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take in the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, let's ride on the tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are saying, you ass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We gotta hurry!\N--Jump into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a bunch of amateurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we turn around now, we'll take the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wave on the side of the ship and capsize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any option.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang tight so you don't get \Nwashed off by the big wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang onto something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My face is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The wave stopped moving!\N--What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has iced in and \Nwe're completely trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must have done by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look down. You can see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Old man...\N--The war has begun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man must have set that \Ntsunami as a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this freezing is the \Nwork of Admiral Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an idea to get us through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hurry! There's less than 3 \Nhours left before Ace's execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want the ship to slide \Ndown this frozen wave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way! First, we gotta \Nget this ship unstuck from the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts? It's a Navy \Nship! We can't lift it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it if we work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that makes me think that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We have the next King of the \NPirates - Captain Buggy on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Captain says that he can \Ndo it, he will do it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all ships and \Nsoldiers! The target is TOTTZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the line and make \Nthe shift to operation 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a Navy operational message.\N--Advance the preparation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TOT... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Must be some kind of code.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are all set,  we \Nmove the schedule forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and execute Ace immediately. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-kun... \N--Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't wait any longer. \NWe don't have time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's get on with Straw boy's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was how Luffy and \Nthe others started falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?! Did a \NNavy ship fall from the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's water, thank god. We fell into water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die \Nby falling on the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't it frozen around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The ship landed in the area \Nwhere Jozu had cleared the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a surprise attack from the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they don't look like the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb! Climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing comparing to \Nthe water torture in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inconvenient that Devil \NFruit eaters can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I fell from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Where are you, Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not on this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Ace! I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Hang on! I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't tell me that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all! Who is in that lineup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All forces are here on both sides! \NThere are a lot of big names!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's got to be ready for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, we're coming to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp! It's your family again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's not only Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei and Ivankov of the \NRevolutionaries army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind them are many infamous pirates, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've escaped from Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always causes trouble... Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What brought him here?\N--And he's not with his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Helmeppo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nothing'll surprise me any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was captured \Nat Impel Down! He's so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought some big faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see him again this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the brother that Ace was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a former and an \Nactive Warlord together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that supposed to be the big \Ntroublemaker rookie--Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat and Crocodile... \NWhy are they together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grandson of the hero--Garp and \Nthe son of the revolutionary--Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, you're working \Nalongside Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your response, Jimbei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is! I resign from The Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd that those people are teaming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prisoners, a commander of \Nthe Revolutionaries army,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some bizarre-looking people and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that they have a common goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Croco boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think he chickened out and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crocodile is aiming for Whitebeard!\N--Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows too well how to fight against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't turn into sand \Nonce you touch water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we are here, our \Nagreement has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to protect Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought--this old man is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace likes this old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's brother is quite a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him come close to Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a strong guy like you \Ncame back after losing an arm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this enemy that you \Ngave your left arm to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put it up for a new generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, squirt, that straw hat you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like the one that \N"Red-Haired" was once wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you know Shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks left it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Pops! This is my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to rescue your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who you're messing with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A squirt like you will be dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That's not up to you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna become the King \Nof the Pirates, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who'll become the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How saucy you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you \Ncause me trouble, spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do as I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-He's competing...\N--...With Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can punish all of them by \Ndeath, can't we, Sengoku-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get there very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Navy HQ, Luffy leads the charge \Nagainst the massive forces there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the men of the Navy attack Luffy in waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace shouts at him to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will Luffy respond to his brother's wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even If It Means Death! \NLuffy vs. the Navy; The Battle Starts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
